notes:
### About

National statistics from Austria.

### Access

No bulk download. Material available in XLS, PDF or HTML formats.

### Data

Fields include:

  * Population
  * Labour Market
  * Health
  * Education, Culture
  * Social Statistics
  * Dwellings, Buildings
  * Agriculture and Forestry
  * Industries and Construction
  * Trade, Services
  * Enterprises (Business Demography)
  * Foreign Trade
  * Tourism
  * Transport
  * Energy, Environment
  * Research and Development (R&D), Innovation
  * Information Society
  * Prices
  * Public Finance, Taxes
  * National Accounts
  * Regional
  * European Indicators

### Openness

Not open. Permission required for redistribution online or commercial re-use. [Website information](http://www.statistik.at/web_en/website_information/index.html) page states:

> The product and the information contained within it are protected by copyright. All rights are reserved by Statistics Austria. Duplication and dissemination of the information and its commercial use is not permitted without the prior written agreement of Statistics Austria. It is furthermore not permitted to place the information on the Internet without the prior written agreement of Statistics Austria, even if the information is provided free of charge. Permitted further use is in any case only allowed if accompanied by a reference to the source “STATISTICS AUSTRIA”.
